summary:
I became Chief Executive Officer of ING Bank Netherlands on April 1 2023. 

Prior to re-joining ING I was a senior partner at McKinsey & Company leading the Technology practice for its European Banking practice. Throughout my consulting years I served banks in Europe, North America and Asia and was primarily focused on digital business building, technology, strategy, and enterprise operating model transformations.

Prior to joining McKinsey, I was Chief Information Officer of ING Bank Netherlands. I have a Ph.D. in Systems Engineering from Delft University of Technology.
